---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Operational Intelligence for Building Materials Distributors"
  description="Data pipelines, real-time dashboards, intelligent alerts, and AI-powered analytics for building materials distributors. Built on top of SAP, NetSuite, and existing ERPs."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
        Operational Intelligence for<br />Building Materials Distributors
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[var(--text-secondary)] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We build the data infrastructure, dashboards, and AI intelligence layer
        that replace your Excel dependency — on top of the ERP you already run.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 1: Real-Time Operational Dashboards -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-[#16A34A]">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
            <polyline points="7 10 10 7 13 10 17 7"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Real-Time Operational Dashboards</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Your team shouldn't wait until Friday to know what happened Monday. We
        build dashboards your purchasing, operations, and finance teams open
        every morning.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Purchasing dashboards:</span> Inventory levels, reorder points, exception management across all warehouses</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Operations dashboards:</span> Warehouse performance, fulfillment metrics, transfer tracking</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Finance dashboards:</span> COGS, landed cost analysis, PO tracking, budget vs. actual</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Real-time data refresh</span> — not weekly Excel exports</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Browser-based</span> — no software to install, accessible from any device</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 2: Modern Data Pipelines -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-[#16A34A]">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="5" cy="6" r="3"></circle>
            <path d="M8 6h8"></path>
            <circle cx="19" cy="6" r="3"></circle>
            <circle cx="5" cy="18" r="3"></circle>
            <path d="M8 18h8"></path>
            <circle cx="19" cy="18" r="3"></circle>
            <path d="M5 9v6"></path>
            <path d="M19 9v6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Modern Data Pipelines</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Your ERP has the data. We build the infrastructure that gets it out —
        automatically, accurately, and continuously.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]">Automated extraction from SAP, NetSuite, or similar ERPs via <span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">ETL/ELT integration</span></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]">Cloud <span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">data warehouse</span> with Bronze/Silver/Gold architecture</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-8">
          <span class="mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-600 shrink-0"></span>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)] font-medium">Bronze Layer:</span> Raw data exactly as it comes from your ERP</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-8">
          <span class="mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#978aa1] shrink-0"></span>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)] font-medium">Silver Layer:</span> Cleaned, validated, and standardized</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-8">
          <span class="mt-2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 shrink-0"></span>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)] font-medium">Gold Layer:</span> Business-ready metrics and KPIs your team actually needs</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">0.00% data variance</span> — our validation standard</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">No manual exports, ever</span></span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 3: Proactive Inventory Alerts -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-[#16A34A]">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"></path>
            <path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"></path>
            <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Proactive Inventory Alerts</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Stop finding out about problems after customers call.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]">Stockout prediction factoring in <span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">overseas lead times (90-120 days)</span> and <span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">domestic suppliers (3-5 days)</span></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]">Safety stock monitoring with automatic exception flagging</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Multi-warehouse visibility</span> — see inventory across all locations in a single view</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Transfer tracking</span> — know what's moving between warehouses and when</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]">Automated alerts <span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">before</span> thresholds are breached</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 4: AI-Powered Intelligence -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-[#22C55E]">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" />
            <path d="M18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455 2.456z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#22C55E] uppercase tracking-wider">Built on your data foundation</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">AI-Powered Intelligence</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Most companies can't do AI because their data isn't clean. We solve the data problem first — then add an AI layer that transforms how your team makes decisions.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#22C55E] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Demand forecasting</span> — AI predicts what you'll need, when, and from which supplier based on historical patterns and lead times</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#22C55E] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Reorder optimization</span> — automatically calculate optimal reorder points factoring in overseas lead times, safety stock, and seasonal demand</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#22C55E] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Margin intelligence</span> — identify which products, customers, and channels are driving margin versus eroding it</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#22C55E] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Natural language queries</span> — ask your data questions in plain English: "What's my stockout risk this month?" and get instant answers</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#22C55E] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-primary-80)]"><span class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium">Anomaly detection</span> — AI watches for patterns your team would miss: unusual pricing trends, supplier reliability shifts, and inventory movement anomalies</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-8 text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm border-l-2 border-[#22C55E]/30 pl-4">
        The AI layer requires a clean data foundation. That's why every engagement starts with the data pipeline and dashboards — then we add intelligence on top. No shortcuts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DON'T DO -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10">What we don't do</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-5">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">We don't replace your ERP. We make it more useful.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">We don't do SAP customization projects. We build an intelligence layer on top.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">We don't build chatbots or AI toys. We build production systems your team runs on daily.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">We don't sell software licenses. You own everything we build.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">We don't subcontract. Vinh architects and builds your system directly.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ENGAGEMENT MODEL -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">How engagements work</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Discovery Call</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#16A34A] font-medium mb-1">30-60 min</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">Complimentary</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-auto">We learn about your operation. No pitch deck.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Paid AI Audit</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#16A34A] font-medium mb-1">2-4 weeks</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-auto">Map every data flow, identify bottlenecks, deliver ROI report.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phased Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#16A34A] font-medium mb-1">8-16 weeks</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-auto">Build pipeline, dashboards, and alerts. Each phase delivers working tools.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm">
        Every engagement starts with the audit. If we can't find enough ROI, we'll tell you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ERP COMPATIBILITY -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--bg-primary)] py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">Works with your existing ERP</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">SAP</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">S/4HANA, ByDesign</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Oracle NetSuite</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Microsoft Dynamics</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">365, GP, NAV</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Epicor</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">Prophet 21, BisTrack, Kinetic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Sage</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">Intacct, X3</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Infor</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">CloudSuite Distribution</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Spruce (ECI)</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">LBM dealers & distributors</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">DMSi Agility</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-1">LBM wholesale</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Acumatica</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">SYSPRO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--glass-bg)] backdrop-blur-xl border border-[var(--glass-border)] rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Odoo</p>
        </div>
